  "description": "Anime adaptation of Kazuyoshi Takeda's <i>Peleliu: Rakuen no Guernica</i> manga.\n<br><br>\nThe story follows the daily lives of Japanese soldiers taking part in the Battle of Peleliu during World War II: a high-casualty, months-long campaign. The main character, Tamaru, dreams of returning home to become a mangaka, and sees their island outpost as a wild paradise that can one day be used as a setting for one of his stories. Most of his comrades, however, are prepared for the more realistic scenario - that they will not be leaving Peleliu alive.",
